---
import SiteShell from '../layouts/SiteShell.astro';
---

<SiteShell title="Privacy Policy" description="Kecker's privacy policy — how we collect and handle information submitted through our contact form.">
  <div class="prose-page">
    <div class="prose-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lede">Plain language. No surprises.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reading-body">
      <p>
        This policy explains what information kecker.co collects when you use this website,
        why we collect it, and how we handle it. We only collect what we need.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        The only personal information we collect is what you voluntarily provide through the
        contact form: your name, email address, company or project name (optional), the area
        of interest you select, and the message you write to us.
      </p>
      <p>
        We also record the IP address of each form submission to help identify and filter spam.
        We do not use it for any other purpose.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not collect device data, browsing behavior, cookies, or any analytics beyond what
        Cloudflare's infrastructure logs automatically as part of serving the site. We do not run
        advertising networks or sell data.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Use It</h2>
      <p>We use contact form submissions only to respond to you directly. That is it.</p>
      <p>
        We do not subscribe you to any mailing list, share your information with third parties,
        or use it for marketing purposes without your explicit consent.
      </p>

      <h2>Where It Is Stored</h2>
      <p>
        Form submissions are stored in a Cloudflare D1 database (SQLite) running on
        Cloudflare's infrastructure. All data is encrypted at rest and in transit.
      </p>

      <h2>How Long We Keep It</h2>
      <p>
        We retain contact form submissions as long as they are relevant to an ongoing
        conversation. You may request deletion of your submission at any time by emailing us.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal
        information we hold about you. Send a request to
        <a href="mailto:frontdoor@kecker.co">frontdoor@kecker.co</a> and we will respond promptly.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted on <a href="https://pages.cloudflare.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Cloudflare Pages</a>.
        Cloudflare may collect standard web server logs (IP address, request path, timestamp) as
        part of serving the site. Please review
        <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a>
        for details on how they handle that data.
      </p>
      <p>We use no other third-party services that receive personal information.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        If we change what we collect or how we use it, we will update this page and revise the
        date below.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Write to us at
        <a href="mailto:frontdoor@kecker.co">frontdoor@kecker.co</a>.
      </p>

      <p><em>Last updated: April 23, 2025</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SiteShell>
